        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 14 at 4:21PM CDT by NWS Austin/San Antonio TX</headline>
        <description>At 421 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Poth, moving northwest at 5 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Floresville, Poth, Stockdale, and Sutherland Springs.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
